# https://github.com/issues based urls give error 404 if user is not logged in.
https://github.com/issues
# https://github.com/*/issues/new* urls redirect to login if user is not logged in.
https://github.com/.*/issues/new.*
# slack.k8s.io is the canonical Kubernetes Slack invite URL and intentionally redirects.
https://slack.k8s.io

# Pages with rigorous bot detection
https://www.dell.com/
https://www.supermicro.com/
